Directed by Shiva Nirvana.

Written by Kona Venkat. Shiva Nirvana. Kona Venkat.

Cast Nani(Uma Maheshwar rao). Nivetha Thomas(Pallavi). Aadhi(Arun (as Aadhi Pinisetty)). Tanikella Bharani(College Professor). Murli Sharma(Pallavi ‘s Father). Prudhviraj(Lovababu) .Master Aarush.Baby Aarushi.Anusha.Master Aryank Bharadhwaj. Gaana Bhat((as Gana Bhat)). Basha Allure Crawford(Princess Jasmine). Amanda Misa Curtis((as Amanda M. Curtis)). Dylan Kento Curtis((as Dylan K. Curtis)).Baby Nayana Ghattamaneni.Naresh Goli.Mac Gurreiro.Sandhya Janak.Baby Janisha.Shashank Kalavala.Anirudh Kasturi.Shiva Kona.Rajesh Konchada.Rajesh Kumar.Srujana Maddhali.Gururaj Manepalli.Divya Mekala.Mounica.Mounika.Ava Mracek.Rajshri Nair.Master Nehanth. Pavan Kumar Pallapunidi((as Pavan Kumar)).Pavan.Phani Pulletikurthi.Shivakumar Ramachandravarapu.Vidyullekha Raman.Phani Rampalli.Dhanish Kumar Reddy.Nimisha Reddy.Shanthi Reddy.Roopani.Sahasra.Sandeep Sandli.Darshana Setty.Kedar Shankar.Meer Shareef.Sheshadri Sridhara.Sudharshan.Jahnavi Swetha. Pawan Tikkisetty((as Pavan Thikkisetty)).Gagan Vihari. VenkataMadhuShankar(Party boy (uncredited))

Language Telugu.

Producers D.V.V. Danayya. Vivek Kuchibhotla. Dev Pinn. Kishore Tatikonda. Kona Venkat.

Production DVV Entertainment. Kona Film Corporation.
